msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:1
#: of
msgid "Make a box plot of the DataFrame columns."
msgstr "制作 DataFrame 列的箱线图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:3
#: of
msgid ""
"A box plot is a method for graphically depicting groups of numerical data"
" through their quartiles. The box extends from the Q1 to Q3 quartile "
"values of the data, with a line at the median (Q2). The whiskers extend "
"from the edges of box to show the range of the data. The position of the "
"whiskers is set by default to 1.5*IQR (IQR = Q3 - Q1) from the edges of "
"the box. Outlier points are those past the end of the whiskers."
msgstr ""
"箱线图是一种通过四分位数来图形化展示数值数据组的方法。箱体从数据的第一"
"四分位数（Q1）延伸到第三四分位数（Q3），中间有一条线表示中位数（Q2）。"
"须线从箱体的边缘延伸，用于显示数据的范围。默认情况下，须线的位置设置为"
"箱体边缘外延 1.5 倍的四分位距（IQR = Q3 - Q1）。超出须线末端的点被视为"
"异常值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:11
#: of
msgid ""
"For further details see Wikipedia's entry for `boxplot "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Box_plot>`__."
msgstr ""
"更多详情请参见维基百科的 `箱线图 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Box_plot>"
"`__ 条目。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:14
#: of
msgid ""
"A consideration when using this chart is that the box and the whiskers "
"can overlap, which is very common when plotting small sets of data."
msgstr ""
"在使用此图表时需要注意的是，箱体和须线可能会重叠，这在绘制小数据集时非常"
"常见。"

